# CODEOWNERS — auto-request review when these paths change
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-security/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# Replace @your-team / @your-handle with real GitHub handles before merging.

# Default reviewers (everything not matched below)
*                       @your-team

# Claude Code config — every change goes through tech leads
.claude/                @your-tech-lead
CLAUDE.md               @your-tech-lead
.mcp.json               @your-tech-lead

# CI / infra
.github/                @your-devops
Dockerfile              @your-devops
docker-compose.yml      @your-devops

# Database migrations — separate sign-off
prisma/migrations/      @your-tech-lead @your-dba
**/migrations/          @your-tech-lead @your-dba

# Security-sensitive files
.claude/rules/security.md   @your-security-lead
.env.example                @your-security-lead

# Documentation
README.md               @your-team
CONTRIBUTING.md         @your-team
docs/                   @your-team
